				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have purchased Pet Affinity with great pleasure (I was afraid of that 20 AA price but it's worthy), but one thing is really annoying me : when a bard in group switches 4 songs, I am getting spammed :
<br />

<br />
Your pet's Warsong of Zek spell has worn off
<br />
Your pet's Rizlona's Call of Flame spell has worn off
<br />
Your pet's Chorus of Marr spell has worn off
<br />
Your pet's Psalm of Veeshan spell has worn off
<br />

<br />
all the time, as the bard isnt refreshing the songs all the time before they wear off.
<br />

<br />
I tried Bard Songs : OFF in the filter menu but it doesn't work.
<br />
I tried to filter Spells -> Worn Off in a window out of the screen, but I like to see other Worn Off messages
<br />

<br />
Any idea what I could do ?<br />_________________<br />Thaumaturge <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=381021" target="_blank" class="postlink">Majax Seplu`Komavan</a>
